        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2716518867" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17311550913273125376">This is a delightful book that will charm adults and children alike. The story captures that timeless magic of an imaginative and happy childhood spent exploring the outdoors experiencing adventures both humorous and frightening with family and friends. This is book 1 of a series and it stands alone with no cliff hangers that leave the reader without a satisfying ending. However I found myself growing very attached to the three-dimensional characters, and enjoyed the author&apos;s writing style so mu</span>
  <span id="freeText17311550913273125376" style="display:none">This is a delightful book that will charm adults and children alike. The story captures that timeless magic of an imaginative and happy childhood spent exploring the outdoors experiencing adventures both humorous and frightening with family and friends. This is book 1 of a series and it stands alone with no cliff hangers that leave the reader without a satisfying ending. However I found myself growing very attached to the three-dimensional characters, and enjoyed the author's writing style so much I have ordered book 2 in the series. The Penderwicks and their summertime adventures made me laugh. I loved every second of this sweet, coming of age story and I highly recommend it.</span>
  <a data-text-id="17311550913273125376" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
